    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">We want to find the coefficients that make this expression work. Better than that, we want to characterize the coefficients so we can predict the value of <em>aₙ.</em></p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
